@startuml
title Sơ đồ tuần tự - Ca sử dụng xác thực OTP đăng ký tài khoản

actor "Khách hàng" as User
boundary "_VerifyOtpScreenState" as VerifyOtpScreenState
control "AuthApiService" as AuthApiService
control "AuthController" as AuthController
control "AuthServiceImpl" as AuthServiceImpl
database "UserRepository" as UserRepository
database "RedisTemplate" as RedisTemplate
control "JwtUtil" as JwtUtil
control "UserMapper" as UserMapper
control "SecurityContextHolder" as SecurityContextHolder
control "Navigator" as Navigator

User -> VerifyOtpScreenState: 1: nhập OTP và bấm Xác thực
activate VerifyOtpScreenState

VerifyOtpScreenState -> VerifyOtpScreenState: 2: _submitOtp(VerifyOtpArgs)
activate VerifyOtpScreenState

VerifyOtpScreenState -> AuthApiService: 3: gọi
activate AuthApiService
AuthApiService -> AuthApiService: 4: verifyOtp(VerifyOtpRequest)
activate AuthApiService

AuthApiService -> AuthController: 5: gọi API POST /auth/otp/verify
activate AuthController
AuthController -> AuthController: 6: verifyOtp(VerifyOtpRequest)
activate AuthController

AuthController -> AuthServiceImpl: 7: gọi
activate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl -> AuthServiceImpl: 8: verifyOtp(VerifyOtpRequest)
activate AuthServiceImpl

AuthServiceImpl -> UserRepository: 9: gọi
activate UserRepository
UserRepository -> UserRepository: 10: findByEmail(email)
activate UserRepository
deactivate UserRepository
UserRepository --> AuthServiceImpl: 11: trả về kết quả
deactivate UserRepository

AuthServiceImpl -> RedisTemplate: 12: gọi
activate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate -> RedisTemplate: 13: opsForValue().get(email)
activate RedisTemplate
deactivate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate --> AuthServiceImpl: 14: trả về kết quả
deactivate RedisTemplate

AuthServiceImpl -> RedisTemplate: 15: gọi
activate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate -> RedisTemplate: 16: delete(email)
activate RedisTemplate
deactivate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate --> AuthServiceImpl: 17: trả về kết quả
deactivate RedisTemplate

AuthServiceImpl -> JwtUtil: 18: gọi
activate JwtUtil
JwtUtil -> JwtUtil: 19: generateToken(User, OtpPurpose)
activate JwtUtil
deactivate JwtUtil
JwtUtil --> AuthServiceImpl: 20: trả về kết quả
deactivate JwtUtil

AuthServiceImpl -> UserMapper: 21: gọi
activate UserMapper
UserMapper -> UserMapper: 22: entityToResponse(User)
activate UserMapper
deactivate UserMapper
UserMapper --> AuthServiceImpl: 23: trả về kết quả
deactivate UserMapper

deactivate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl --> AuthController: 24: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthServiceImpl

deactivate AuthController
AuthController --> AuthApiService: 25: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthController

deactivate AuthApiService
AuthApiService --> VerifyOtpScreenState: 26: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthApiService

VerifyOtpScreenState -> AuthApiService: 27: gọi
activate AuthApiService
AuthApiService -> AuthApiService: 28: activeAccount(token)
activate AuthApiService

AuthApiService -> AuthController: 29: gọi API POST /auth/active
activate AuthController
AuthController -> AuthController: 30: activeAccount(token)
activate AuthController

AuthController -> AuthServiceImpl: 31: gọi
activate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl -> AuthServiceImpl: 32: activeAccount(token)
activate AuthServiceImpl

AuthServiceImpl -> SecurityContextHolder: 33: gọi
activate SecurityContextHolder
SecurityContextHolder -> SecurityContextHolder: 34: getContext().getAuthentication().getName()
activate SecurityContextHolder
deactivate SecurityContextHolder
SecurityContextHolder --> AuthServiceImpl: 35: trả về kết quả
deactivate SecurityContextHolder

AuthServiceImpl -> UserRepository: 36: gọi
activate UserRepository
UserRepository -> UserRepository: 37: findByEmailAndActive(email, false)
activate UserRepository
deactivate UserRepository
UserRepository --> AuthServiceImpl: 38: trả về kết quả
deactivate UserRepository

AuthServiceImpl -> JwtUtil: 39: gọi
activate JwtUtil
JwtUtil -> JwtUtil: 40: getClaims(token)
activate JwtUtil
deactivate JwtUtil
JwtUtil --> AuthServiceImpl: 41: trả về kết quả
deactivate JwtUtil

AuthServiceImpl -> RedisTemplate: 42: gọi
activate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate -> RedisTemplate: 43: opsForValue().set(claims.id, token, ttl)
activate RedisTemplate
deactivate RedisTemplate
RedisTemplate --> AuthServiceImpl: 44: trả về kết quả
deactivate RedisTemplate

AuthServiceImpl -> JwtUtil: 45: gọi
activate JwtUtil
JwtUtil -> JwtUtil: 46: generateToken(User)
activate JwtUtil
deactivate JwtUtil
JwtUtil --> AuthServiceImpl: 47: trả về kết quả
deactivate JwtUtil

AuthServiceImpl -> UserMapper: 48: gọi
activate UserMapper
UserMapper -> UserMapper: 49: entityToResponse(User)
activate UserMapper
deactivate UserMapper
UserMapper --> AuthServiceImpl: 50: trả về kết quả
deactivate UserMapper

deactivate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl --> AuthController: 51: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthServiceImpl

deactivate AuthController
AuthController --> AuthApiService: 52: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthController

deactivate AuthApiService
AuthApiService --> VerifyOtpScreenState: 53: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthApiService

VerifyOtpScreenState -> Navigator: 54: gọi
activate Navigator
Navigator -> Navigator: 55: pushNamedAndRemoveUntil(AppRoutes.login)
activate Navigator
deactivate Navigator
Navigator --> VerifyOtpScreenState: 56: trả về kết quả
deactivate Navigator

deactivate VerifyOtpScreenState

VerifyOtpScreenState --> User: 57: điều hướng về màn hình đăng nhập
deactivate VerifyOtpScreenState

@enduml
